  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(* --- Fully assembled untwisted transfer-matrix eigenvalues on irrep mu ---\n   All anchored at the pseudovacuum (mu_top=[S+P,S+P,0,0]); Delta-Cas measured from there.\n   tau1 : vacuum + (h^2/2) DeltaCas2                                   [only Cas2]\n   tau3 : same (h^2/2)DeltaCas2 structure times its trivial factor      [only Cas2]\n   tau2 : vacuum + (h^2/8)DeltaCas2 [t1vac(u)+t1vac(u-h)]  (fusion form, matches u^2 & u^1 exactly)\n          + h^4 (1/8 DeltaCas2^2 - 1/4 DeltaCas4)          [the Cas4-carrying constant, known structure]\n   Verified: tau1's b1 = asympSol; tau2's u^2,u^1 coeffs = asympSol; tau2(mu_top)=t2vac. *)\nCas2top = Cas2[mutop]; Cas4top = Cas4[mutop];\nt1vac[uu_] := Sum[nu[i][uu], {i, 4}];\ntau1[mu_][u_] := t1vac[u] + (h^2/2) (Cas2[mu] - Cas2top);\ntau2[mu_][u_] := t2vac[u] + (h^2/8) (Cas2[mu] - Cas2top) (t1vac[u] + t1vac[u - h])\n   + h^4 (1/8 (Cas2[mu]^2 - Cas2top^2) - 1/4 (Cas4[mu] - Cas4top));\n(* consistency battery (all must be 0) *)\n{Simplify[Coefficient[tau1[{m1,m2,m3,m4}][u], u, 0] - ((b[1] /. asympSol) /. b[2] -> b2gen[{m1,m2,m3,m4}])],\n Simplify[Coefficient[tau2[{m1,m2,m3,m4}][u], u, 2] - b2gen[{m1,m2,m3,m4}]],\n Simplify[Coefficient[tau2[{m1,m2,m3,m4}][u], u, 1] - ((c[2] /. asympSol) /. b[2] -> b2gen[{m1,m2,m3,m4}])],\n Simplify[(Coefficient[tau2[{m1,m2,m3,m4}][u], u, 0] /. {m1->S+P,m2->S+P,m3->0,m4->0}) - d2vac]}",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"342126\" data-output-id=\"6\" data-out-n=\"40\" data-sub-idx=\"6\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"8\" data-sub-start=\"13\" data-sub-end=\"16\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[40]=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mru9aw9p-9ubtnj2\" data-page-width-em=\"22\" data-latex-b64=\"XGxlZnRcezAsMCwwLDBccmlnaHRcfQ==\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">{</span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">}</span></span></span></span></span></span></div></div></div></div>",
       "mime": "x-application/wolfram-language-html"
      },
      {
       "data": "Out[40]= \\left\\{0,0,0,0\\right\\}",
       "mime": "text/plain"
      }
     ],
     "id": "aed3a694-12c3-459f-9718-fc7985011412"
    }
