       "data": "Out[60]= \\left\\{\\left\\{1\\right\\},\\left\\{0,-\\theta1-\\theta2,1\\right\\},\\left\\{0,-h^2-3\\,\\theta1\\,\\theta2,0,1\\right\\},\\left\\{0,\\frac{1}{2}\\,\\left(-2\\,h^4+5\\,h^2\\,\\theta1^2+10\\,h^2\\,\\theta1\\,\\theta2+5\\,h^2\\,\\theta2^2+30\\,\\theta1^2\\,\\theta2^2\\right),0,0,-\\frac{5}{2}\\,\\left(\\theta1+\\theta2\\right),1\\right\\}\\right\\}",
