       "data": "Join::heads: Heads List and Equal at positions 1 and 3 are expected to be the same.\nTable::iterb: Iterator {j, 0, {2, 1, 1, 0}} does not have appropriate bounds.\nTable::iterb: Iterator {j, 0, {2, 1, 1, 0}} does not have appropriate bounds.\nSolve::naqs: Join[{gaudinODE == 0}, {cq[{2, 1, 1, 0}] == 1}, degQ[] == 0] is not a quantified system of equations and inequalities.\nTable::iterb: Iterator {j, 0, {2, 1, 1, 0}} does not have appropriate bounds.\nGeneral::stop: Further output of Table::iterb will be suppressed during this calculation.\nReplaceAll::reps: {Join[{gaudinODE == 0}, {cq[{2, 1, 1, 0}] == 1}, degQ[] == 0]} is neither a list of replacement rules nor a valid dispatch table, and so cannot be used for replacing.\nJoin::heads: Heads List and Equal at positions 1 and 3 are expected to be the same.\nSolve::naqs: Join[{gaudinODE == 0}, {cq[1] == 1}, degQ[cq[{2, 1, 1, 0}]] == 0] is not a quantified system of equations and inequalities.\nReplaceAll::reps: {Join[{gaudinODE == 0}, {cq[1] == 1}, degQ[cq[{2, 1, 1, 0}]] == 0]} is neither a list of replacement rules nor a valid dispatch table, and so cannot be used for replacing.\nJoin::heads: Heads List and Equal at positions 1 and 3 are expected to be the same.\nGeneral::stop: Further output of Join::heads will be suppressed during this calculation.\nSolve::naqs: Join[{gaudinODE == 0}, {cq[1] == 1}, degQ[cq[{2, 1, 1, 0}], cq[1]] == 0] is not a quantified system of equations and inequalities.\nGeneral::stop: Further output of Solve::naqs will be suppressed during this calculation.\nReplaceAll::reps: {Join[{gaudinODE == 0}, {cq[1] == 1}, degQ[cq[{2, 1, 1, 0}], cq[1]] == 0]} is neither a list of replacement rules nor a valid dispatch table, and so cannot be used for replacing.\nGeneral::stop: Further output of ReplaceAll::reps will be suppressed during this calculation.\nPart::partw: Part 4 of degQ[{2, 1, 1, 0}, 1, 1] does not exist.",
